## Feature Breakdown (Phased)

### Phase 1 — Core MVP (Week 1-2)
- [ ] "Tap to Add Payment" screen — amount, merchant, category picker
- [ ] Payment list (today's transactions)
- [ ] Daily summary card (total spent, transaction count, category pie chart)
- [ ] Encrypted local database setup
- [ ] Dark mode support
- [ ] Default currency: **CAD** (Canadian Dollar)

### Phase 2 — Enhanced Tracking (Week 3)
- [ ] Multiple card support (last 4 digits identification)
- [ ] Search and filter payments by date range
- [ ] Category-based spending breakdown with charts
- [ ] Daily budget alerts (push notification when threshold hit)
- [ ] Export daily summary as PDF (generated on-device, not uploaded)

### Phase 3 — Smart Features (Week 4)
- [ ] Recurring payment detection and reminders
- [ ] Spending trends (week-over-week comparison)
- [ ] Quick-add from notification (log payment without opening app)
- [ ] Widget for iOS/Android home screen showing today's spend

### Phase 4 — Security & Future (Post-Launch)
- [ ] **Biometric lock screen on app launch** (Face ID / Fingerprint)
- [ ] Bank SMS parsing (auto-detect payments from bank texts — opt-in)
- [ ] Optional encrypted cloud backup (user-controlled E2E encryption key)
- [ ] Multi-currency support with offline conversion rates

