## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
# Unit tests for all services and utils
npx jest --coverage

# Specific security tests
npx jest __tests__/services/EncryptionService.test.ts
npx jest __tests__/services/PaymentValidator.test.ts
```

### Security Verification
- [ ] Run `npx expo-doctor` to check for known vulnerabilities
- [ ] Verify no sensitive data appears in `console.log` output
- [ ] Test app behavior on background/foreground transitions (biometric re-prompt)
- [ ] Verify encrypted DB file is unreadable without the app context

### Manual Verification
- [ ] Add 5+ payments and verify daily summary accuracy
- [ ] Kill app and reopen — verify biometric prompt appears
- [ ] Take screenshot while app is open — verify it's blocked/blurred
- [ ] Check that exported PDF contains correct data

